Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.36,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.70,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}We've got scars to prove we're too
